# Deploy (ridelogger-mcp)

## Remote server

- **Host**: 159.89.22.200
- **App path**: `/var/www/ridelogger-mcp` (git checkout, venv, `.env`)
- **systemd**: `ridelogger-mcp.service` — pokreće `python -m ridelogger_mcp` kao `www-data`, sluša **`127.0.0.1:8083`**
- **Apache**: reverse proxy za **`mcp.ridelogger.com`** (primarni) i `mcp.servisna-knjizica.com` (legacy alias) → `http://127.0.0.1:8083/` (TLS preko Certbot-a; HTTP → HTTPS redirect)
- **Javni URL (primarni)**: `https://mcp.ridelogger.com` — health `GET /health`, MCP streamable HTTP **`https://mcp.ridelogger.com/mcp`**
- **Legacy URL**: `https://mcp.servisna-knjizica.com/mcp` i dalje radi na istom backend-u (za postojeće MCP klijente)

Port **8083** nije izložen javno; samo loopback + Apache.

## Konfiguracija na serveru

- **`/var/www/ridelogger-mcp/.env`** (ne commitovati), primarni ridelogger.com setup:
  ```
  SK_API_URL=https://api.ridelogger.com
  OAUTH_AUTHORIZATION_SERVER=https://api.ridelogger.com
  OAUTH_RESOURCE_URL=https://mcp.ridelogger.com/mcp
  OPENAI_APPS_CHALLENGE_TOKEN=<OpenAI Platform → MCP Server → Domain verification → Token>
  MCP_HOST=127.0.0.1
  MCP_PORT=8083
  API_CONSUMER_CODE=mcp
  API_CONSUMER_KEY_ID=<k_... iz api_consumers tabele>
  API_CONSUMER_SECRET=<secret iz api_consumers tabele>
  ```
- Isti fajl koristi **systemd** (`EnvironmentFile=-/var/www/ridelogger-mcp/.env`)

## Ažuriranje posle izmene koda (tipičan deploy)

SSH, pa u app direktorijumu pull, reinstall ako se promenile zavisnosti, restart servisa:

```bash
ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_openclaw -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@159.89.22.200
cd /var/www/ridelogger-mcp
sudo -u www-data git pull
sudo -u www-data .venv/bin/pip install .
systemctl restart ridelogger-mcp
```

Provera:

```bash
curl -fsS https://mcp.ridelogger.com/health
curl -fsS https://mcp.ridelogger.com/.well-known/oauth-protected-resource | jq .
journalctl -u ridelogger-mcp -n 50 --no-pager
```

## Apache / TLS

- Vhost fajlovi: `/etc/apache2/sites-available/mcp.ridelogger.com.conf` (HTTP) + `mcp.ridelogger.com-le-ssl.conf` (HTTPS, Certbot). Legacy aliasi za `mcp.servisna-knjizica.com` postoje pored njih.
- Posle ručne izmene Apache konfiguracije: `apache2ctl configtest && systemctl reload apache2`.
- Sertifikat: obnavlja **certbot** (`certbot renew` / systemd timer); nije potrebno ručno osim debug-a.

## Napomene

- Ako se doda Python paket u `pyproject.toml`, uvek **`pip install .`** posle pull-a pre restart-a.
- Za debug logove MCP protokola (više šuma): u `.env` privremeno `MCP_VERBOSE_LOGS=true`, pa `systemctl restart ridelogger-mcp`.
